The TRANSFORMERS are back, and this time they're in the hands of acclaimed
developer PlatinumGames, who has married their over-the-top, stylish
action with a major dose of nostalgia to create a TRANSFORMERS game

discovers a way to harness the enormous power of Plasma Energy to
Cyberform Earth.
